# default()

**Type Method**

Returns the default subscription registration center object.

## Declaration

```swift
class func `default`() -> VSSubscriptionRegistrationCenter
```

## Return Value

This method returns a [doc://com.apple.videosubscriberaccount/documentation/VideoSubscriberAccount/VSSubscriptionRegistrationCenter] object that refers to the default registration center.

## Discussion

Use the object this method returns to tell the system what content the user is able to access within your app.
